Stop it.

756
00:34:02,870 --> 00:34:03,910
I found another new project.

757
00:34:03,910 --> 00:34:05,035
We must invest in it this time.

758
00:34:05,035 --> 00:34:07,150
Sometimes, Mr. Ma's preference
does leave me in awe.

759
00:34:07,630 --> 00:34:09,220
