815
00:35:56,124 --> 00:35:57,540
I won't agree with this. No way.

816
00:35:58,020 --> 00:35:58,790
That's enough.

817
00:35:58,790 --> 00:35:59,700
Why get so agitated?

818
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:00,620
